Steven Knight -LRB- born 1959 -RRB- is a British screenwriter and film director .
He read English at University College London -LRB- UCL -RRB- .
Knight has written the screenplays for the films Closed Circuit , Dirty Pretty Things and Eastern Promises , and also directed as well as written the films Locke and Hummingbird -LRB- a.k.a. Redemption -RRB- .
Knight is also one of three creators of Who Wants to Be a Millionaire ?
, a game show that has been remade and aired in around 160 countries worldwide , and has written for BBC 's Commercial Breakdown , The Detectives , Peaky Blinders and Taboo .